title: Think in Black & White
itunes:title: Think in Black & White
description:
Episode 175 - Do you tend to overcomplicate situations by thinking too much? Either you do something or you don't. If you think and worry about everything, you are still NOT doing it! There is no need to overcomplicate. Think in black and white, either you do it or you don't. And if you don't, then move on to the next thing and keep going!
